
LCS/AMC/AMCBase package
=======================

This package is one of two packages that together form the Astronomical
Measures Conversions (AMC) package. It contains the interface definition of
the conversion methods and some basic classes that define sky coordinates,
earth coordinates (position on earth) and time. Furthermore, it contains the
implementation of the client side of the AMC client/server.



Required packages:
-----------------

internal: 
  LCS/Common (2.2)
  LCS/Transport (2.0)

